lines: 1. Ruodha, aheri maradier,Moloyo mor mar piny;Nikech imiya kuwe mariMa piny ok nyal ketho.
To ji mang`eny pok ong`eyo (ong`eyo) Herani modhiero;To ji mang`eny pok ong`enyo (ong`eyo) Rembi moseluoka (oluoka).
2. Ang`eyo Intie buta, Ruoth, Moloyo ji me piny;Kaparoi ayudo mor Moloyona mor piny.
3. Iketo morni e chunya, Ma piny ok nyal golo;Da ok abed gi herani, Kuyo dipong` chunya.
4. Kwayudo mor e ngimawa Kwawuotho kodi ka,To wanayud mor manade Kwaneni Wang` gi Wang`.
